OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry this
OL,6,Fevening with some late bright periods.
OL,7,FMeanwhile light and patchy rain
OL,8,Fspreads in to affect western areas,
OL,9,Fbut most places in the east remaining
OL,10,Fdry.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FCloudy with a few spots of
OL,13,Flight rain, but mainly dry with some
OL,14,Fbrighter spells for Moray. Outbreaks
OL,15,Fof rain will then spread northeast
OL,16,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
